Package: epimutacions
Title: Robust outlier identification for DNA methylation data
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Leire",family = "Abarrategui",role = c("aut", "cre"),email = "nla94@newcastle.ac.uk"),
      person("Juan R.", "Gonzalez", ,"juanr.gonzalez@isglobal.org", role = "aut"),
      person("Carlos", "Ruiz-Arenas", ,"carlos.ruiza@upf.edu", role = "aut"),
      person("Carles", "Hernandez-Ferrer", ,"carles.hernandez@cnag.crg.eu", role = "aut"))
Description: The package includes several functions for outlier detection in DNA methylation data. It also contains epimutation (rare alterations in the methylation pattern at specific loci) annotation and visualization functions. 
